@group accounts
@endpoint POST /accounts/{accountId}/rooms/{roomId}/memberships?operation=batch-create
@desc Adds up to 50 members to a chat room in an Amazon Chime Enterprise account. Members can be users or bots. The member role designates whether the member is a chat room administrator or a general chat room member.
